					"type": 23,
					"value": "Nightsong speaks with Shadowheart about Shadowheart's parents, causing Shadowheart to remember the truth. Shadowheart reflects that she needs to recover her memories in Baldur's Gate. Nightsong gives Shadowheart an artifact and a blessing."
